tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE shopping_behavior (
  customer_id INT,
  purchase_date DATE,
  purchased_item VARCHAR,
  category VARCHAR,
  price DECIMAL,
  quantity INT
)

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE purchases (
    purchase_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL,
    purchase_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    calories INT,
    fat_g INT,
    sugar_g INT
)
CREATE TABLE Users (user_id INT PRIMARY KEY, username VARCHAR(50), email VARCHAR(100), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10));
CREATE TABLE Products (product_id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_name VARCHAR(50), category VARCHAR(50), price DECIMAL(10, 2), is_healthy BOOLEAN);
CREATE TABLE Orders (order_id INT PRIMARY KEY, user_id INT, order_date DATE, total_price DECIMAL(10, 2), FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES Users(user_id));

CREATE TABLE Recommendations (recommendation_id INT PRIMARY KEY, user_id INT, product_id INT, recommendation_date DATE, FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES Users(user_id), FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES Products(product_id));

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL(10,2),
    calories INT,
    is_organic BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE purchases (
    purchase_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    purchase_date TIMESTAMP,
    quantity INT,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE suggestions (
    suggestion_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    suggested_product_id INT,
    suggested_date TIMESTAMP,
    suggested_category VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE meal_plans (
    plan_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    plan_name VARCHAR(100),
    plan_description TEXT,
    plan_type VARCHAR(50)
);
